IS NULL
Write a query to display all reactions where the comment is missing (i.e., NULL).
select reaction_type from reaction where comment is null;
+---------------+
| reaction_type |
+---------------+
| angry         |
| sad           |
| like          |
| sad           |
| like          |
| wow           |
| like          |
| angry         |
