IS NOT NULL
Write a query to find all reactions that include a comment.
select reaction_type from reaction where comment is not null;
+---------------+
| reaction_type |
+---------------+
| like          |
| love          |
| wow           |
| love          |
| like          |
| angry         |
| love          |
